      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KING FENCER (4) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Other three back before a placing at this track the following run. Better than latest and can atone here. WELLINGTON SALIX (2) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 515m behind Stella Shadows (31.34) in a Special conditions race. Was in the money the start prior. Key runner on best form. HIGHGATE BUSTER (5) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at Hobart over 340m (19.77) after charging straight to the lead, scoring by a nose. Expected to be in the finish. WHERE'S AUNTY (3) was below best last time at Hobart (26.33) in a Grade 5, finishing a 9 length sixth. Has already won three times from this draw.",
